# Test Enforcement And Guardrails

- After every completed code change, run the full project test suites before reporting done:
  - Backend: `cd backend && ./venv/bin/python -m pytest -q`
  - Frontend: `cd frontend && npm test`
- If tests fail, fix production code first and rerun tests until green.
- Never delete tests to make the suite pass.
- Do not modify test files unless the user explicitly approves test edits in the current chat.
- When test files were changed with approval, state that clearly in the final response.
